  $ add_synced_commit_mapping_entry 1 $WITH_MERGE_MARKER 0 $MEGAREPO_MARKER

Preserve commits from with_merge
  $ add_synced_commit_mapping_entry 1 $WITH_MERGE_C1 0 $WITH_MERGE_C1
